You no fit tell me say that stew wey you Dey take chop rice never tire you. Oya try this one you go like am.

See as my pepper fine well well, na @buchymix food processor run am oo🤩🤩..

Ingredients;
*Goatmeat(seasoned with paprika, seasoning powder,curry and thyme, Ginger and onions)
*More of Tatashe, scotch bonnets, onions and fresh garlic).
*Fried plantain
*Bell peppers
Cook goatmeat till liquid dries up then fry slightly.
Make sure you season goat meat appropriately so that you don’t have to season again when frying the peppermix.
